# Auto-generated finding drafts are transient — they're overwritten on
# every `barista-netanalyze` run and promoted into the parent catalog
# directory when a reviewer accepts them. Ignore every markdown file
# except the README that documents how the directory works. A
# maintainer can `git add -f <draft>.md` to pin a long-lived draft;
# the bias is to promote or discard rather than pin.
*.md
!README.md
